author: @ER.j
text:
Mark, your voice calms me down and makes me want to live. Thank you for being my love for many years. Thanks to you, I can walk with relief and smile. You make my life brighter. Thank you for always shining on my dark side. In a world full of suffering, at least I have you, so I don't despair. Thank you, and I always love you Mark 
Love from Ukraine

author: @ER.j
text:
Mark, I would like to thank you properly, because for a long time you have been giving me comfort. You are a great comfort to me and I am the person who is strong, thanks to you! Your music and your words have become my light and just looking at you, knowing that you are somewhere on the other side of the planet is already a great happiness. One day I'd like to hug you. But even if it's impossible, every time I send you a mental hug and give you all my love. Thank you that your voice accompanies me in my life and you give me a lot of joy. Although I don't speak your language, you are my biggest attachment in my dark world. Thank you for being my comfort for so many years. I hope to be with you in the future and continue to love you forever. Thank you for teaching me how to love.. Mark Lee
From Ukraine
